data.title: :: Barentsnight Garbo's Ninotchka
data.text:
Born: April 18, 2013

Sire : CH UKC, ABIDS Nibelung Yablunevyi Tsvit "Benia", TT, CGN

HU: N/N, JLPP: Clear

Dam : GCH CKC, CH IABCA Barents Night Bella Donna, CGN - #1 CKC Conformation BRT in Canada, 2016

HU:N/HU, JLPP: Clear

Owner: Link Roberts, Tatiana & Doug Adams

Nina is soft, kind, very friendly, playful, lovable & so feminine girl. Wish to please every one.

Loves people, dogs and see every one as a friend. Very smart with high working ability.

Beautiful body structure, black rich coat, dark eyes, perfect bite, dark pigment, nice black harsh coat. Excellent angulation, absolutely stunning movement and great temperament.

We are so pleased with puppies what she gave to us. As a mother they are stunning.

Height 73 cm, weight 120 LB

HU: N/N

JLPP: Clear

Nina's Health Page Click Here

Nina & Travis gave to us beautiful show/working dogs:

- BarentsNight Magnolia

- CH CKC, CH UKC BarentsNight Object of Art "Zorro", CGN, RN, RI, CGC, CGCA, CGCU

- CH CKC, CH UKC BarentsNight Ophelia "Livi", CGN

- Barents Night One in a Million "Monty"

- Barents Night Oscar Winner "Nicco", CGN

- Barents Night Odyssey "Leo", CGN

- Barents Night Orion Nebula "Jake"
